{
  "texts": [
    "Let us label this inference schema \"I A.\"",
    "This (deductively invalid, as desired) schema accords with many of the simple, familiar specimens of abduction.",
    "For example, suppose that soon after waking in the morning Bertram goes to the kitchen to make a cup of coffee, but upon entering the room finds a steaming cup of cappuccino sitting on his placemat at the breakfast table.",
    "No one else is present.",
    "Bertram asks himself: How did this situation come to be?"
  ]
}